Docker container are temporary
- i.e if container is deleted data within container is also deleted.

We will map a folder inside container - with a folder on local laptop
 - i.e folder on local laptop becomes persistent storage

Demo steps:
-Create container
-Add a file inside container
-Delete container
-Create new container
-Verify file is still available in new container. 

